Transform your browser start page with the whimsical Hello Kitty in Space Theme extension! Every new tab features images of Hello Kitty exploring the cosmos, adding a touch of fun and adventure to your browsing experience. Enjoy delightful scenes of Hello Kitty in space, making each new tab a charming and interstellar experience.
This extension allows you to chose your search engine.
